{"article_id":"RRqD14yDMIgl1Lmx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"SEOUL -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"South Korean President Moon Jae-in said Sunday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that Kim Jong Un expressed a firm commitment","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to complete denuclearization of the Korean Peninsula","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and that the North Korean leader still wants to meet with President Trump .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Moon briefed reporters on his surprise Saturday meeting with Kim ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"which took place on the North Korean side of the Panmunjom border village inside the Demilitarized Zone","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that divides the peninsula .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"In what Moon described as a \" candid , heart-to-heart conversation , \"","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"he said","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Kim \" made clear once again","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"his intentions","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to completely denuclearize the Korean Peninsula , \"","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and expressed a willingness","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"\" to put an end to the history of war and confrontation through the success of the North Korea-United States summit . \"","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"After secret North and South Korea meeting ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Trump says","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"summit talks going 'well '","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Trump again changes tone on North Korea :","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"'We are talking to them now '","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"North Korea :","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Trump 's cancellation of meeting was 'unexpected '","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"but we 're still willing to talk","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Meanwhile , an American delegation met with North Koreans officials Sunday in the DMZ ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"as planning seemed to move ahead for the Trump-Kim summit .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Saturday 's unannounced meeting between the two Korean leaders came a month after their first summit ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"held April 27 on the South Korean side of Panmunjom .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Moon said","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Kim on Friday had requested to meet him","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"\" without any formality , \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"and the casual nature of the second meeting was \" like a normal routine between friends . \"","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"The meeting seemed to push momentum toward a summit between Trump and Kim to take place ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"which would be the first time","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"a sitting U.S. president would meet with a North Korean leader .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Trump on Thursday abruptly called off the meeting ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"which was scheduled for June 12 in Singapore ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"with a letter to Kim","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"citing the \" tremendous anger and open hostility \" of recent communications from Pyongyang .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Trump changed course less than 24 hours later ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"tweeting on Friday","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"that Washington was having \" very productive talks '' with North Korea","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"about reinstating the summit , possibly on the same date and location .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Trump repeated that position Saturday night .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"`` We 're looking at June 12th in Singapore .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"That has n't changed , ''","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Trump said in the Oval Office","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"as he welcomed freed American Joshua Holt after his release from Venezuela .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Moon said","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"that during his meeting with Kim , he delivered the message","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that Trump still has \" a firm resolve","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"to put an end to hostility against North Korea","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"and work for economic cooperation with the North \"","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"if Pyongyang completely denuclearizes .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"\" I emphasized","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"that it is necessary for the two sides to engage in direct talks","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"to eliminate misunderstandings","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"and have sufficient preliminary , working-level negotiations","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"concerning the agenda","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"that needs to be agreed upon at the summit , \"","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Moon said ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"that Kim agreed .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"The South Korean president said","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"the U.S. and North Korea would hold the working-level talks very soon","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"to determine","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"whether the summit would go forward .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"If the summit is successfully held ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Moon said","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"he hoped to follow up with a three-way meeting with the two Koreas and the U.S.","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to \" formally end the ( Korean ) War . \"","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"The Korean War ceased in 1953 with an armistice but not a peace treaty .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"North Korea ' s official state news agency also expressed","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Kim ' s desire","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"to meet with Trump .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"In a statement","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"released Sunday ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Kim \" expressed his fixed will \"","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"to hold the summit with Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"the Korean Central News Agency said .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":163,"left":0,"right":162,"relation":"organization","